personal glory vein in him to ruin it for you know hundreds of thousands of other people for you know years to come and I don't think that he I mean he's I'm sure his bottom line is make sure that you maintain a captive audience at the San Francisco Public Library we need them to keep buying you know those computers we need to maintain those lines and have them pay for them and I think that that's that's what his big trip is I don't believe very much that Steve Colter really gives a shit we have a literate society

