41:27.470 --> 41:28.371
And I said, OK.

41:28.823 --> 41:29.985
You know, I think L.A.

41:30.005 --> 41:32.269
probably has some special collections.

41:32.470 --> 41:40.585
But anyway, her attitude is that it's not the mission of the public library to be a research library.

41:40.725 --> 41:43.871
Let's tell that to Shaw and Virginia Woolf.

41:44.452 --> 41:46.014
Well, I mean, whatever, you know.

41:46.295 --> 41:52.065
You know, like Marie Sundeck, who are totally the product of their reading, you know, at libraries.

41:52.186 --> 41:52.907
Right, I'm sorry.

41:53.343 --> 41:56.047
I mean, I think that the attitude is fine.

41:56.087 --> 41:57.650
If we're going to shift gears, that's fine.

41:57.690 --> 42:01.937
I know that the municipal funds are shrinking or whatever, or not even whatever.

42:01.957 --> 42:11.352
