42:50.771 --> 42:54.014
It's in, I don't know, I wish I, I mean, this is bringing up a lot.

42:54.034 --> 43:01.521
I was starting to feel a little bit better about being here, but it just, I am, I'm actually, I'm very angry at what's happened here.

43:01.940 --> 43:10.675
