43:44.829 --> 43:47.613
I mean, the class was cracking up, because I said I'd left.

43:48.034 --> 43:52.500
I used to work for Congresswoman Pelosi, and I said I'd left that job, and I came to the library looking for refuge.

43:52.480 --> 43:58.530
and suddenly here I am again, you know, I'm in the middle of this political stuff, and they all started laughing.

