um actually right now at city college and planning and transfers in san francisco state and how old are you 27. terry olson is 85. i could have fallen down yeah i didn't know that's great i damn near collapsed she was wonderful there's one thing i want to say is like as far as the discretion as far as what books were read it or not um claire pointed out that

